ourscomen-usproductslinefloor-heating-tempzone-cablereferral_codekricom&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.warmlyyours.com/en-US/products/line/floor-heating-tempzone-cable?referral_code=KRICOM&#34;&gt;TempZone™ 3.7-Watt Floor Heating Cable:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  img {&#xA;    width: 50%;&#xA;  }&#xA;&#xA;  @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {&#xA;    p {&#xA;      font-size: 16px;&#xA;      display: inline;&#xA;    }&#xA;&#xA;    img {&#xA;      width: 100%;&#xA;      height: auto;&#xA;    }&#xA;  }&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;display: flex;justify-content: center;max-width:100%;height:auto;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;figure style=&#34;display: table;margin:0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;postImage mx-auto&#34; alt=&#34;TempZone™ 3.7-Watt Floor Heating Cable&#34;&#xA; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/installationOptions/warmlyYours/tempzone-cable-29c541.jpeg 324w, http://localhost:1313/img/installationOptions/warmlyYours/tempzone-cable-29c541.jpeg 720w&#34;&#xA; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) 324w, 720w&#34;&#xA; src=&#34;https://ik.imagekit.io/wy/kri//img/installationOptions/warmlyYours/tempzone-cable-29c541.jpeg&#34;&#xA; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA; style=&#34;max-width: 100%; height: auto;&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;ficaption style=&#34;display: table-caption;caption-side: bottom;text-align: center;font-size: .7rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/ficaption&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;The WarmlyYours TempZone™ 3.7-Watt Floor Heating Cable allows you to bring radiant warmth to any room. TempZone™ Floor Heating Cable (Twin) is ultra-low EMF by design. It features a twin conductor with a 15’ cold lead and is available in two voltage options and a range of lengths to meet the requirements of any installation. In 120V, we offer lengths ranging from 30 to 432 linear feet . For 240V, our lengths range from 55 to 864 linear feet.&amp;rdquo; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
